item.title: News-May-2018
item.description: Meetup #4 on June 7 @ ImpactHub We will have our fourth meetup on June 7, 2018, 6:30 pm at ImpactHub. During one hour we will have four speakers talking about four topics, each presentation will be 10-20 min long. You can register to attend and … we are still looking for two more speakers! So get in touch with us! R-Ladies Lausanne has a Webpage! Click on subscribe to enable the RSS feed for this site.
